item.description:
At times the pub is fairly empty and others it's fairly packed. The quiz starts at 8pm and typically ends at 10pm. You can have a team of up to 5 people...

Again, this is just a social, nothing more. However, for those that cannot attend the Dover Wednesday socials, this is another opportunity to meet the members.

Other benefits are (1) typically free appetizers after 9pm and (2) if you come in 1st or 2nd place the team gets a discount on their tab.
item.name: Portsmouth Social / Pub Quiz
